cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is primarily focused on image restoration tasks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper proposes a new convolutional neural network architecture that incorporates scale-invariance into the restoration process, which is a topic of interest in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed model on multiple image restoration tasks, which could also fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
